thread.title: Eve Mikazuki

author: Eve Mikazuki
title: Eve Mikazuki
text: I had no issues getting my custom calendar and I appreciate the options in their creation engine. The only negative that keep me from giving a 5/5 is that the delivery took so damned long. I missed a month on the calendar because it had to take 2 weeks. Other than that it's a great service and the quality is what you upload. They also warn you that the resolution of your images are too low but let you use it anyway if you insist. Very user friendly.
